<li>Thinking of you and sending my deepest condolences.</li>
<li>Your friend was a special person, and they will be missed.</li>
<li>I'm here for you, whatever you need.</li>
<li>May you find peace and comfort in the memories you shared.</li>
<li>I’ll always cherish the memories we shared with [friend's name].</li>
<li>Your loss is deeply felt.  I'm here to listen if you need to talk.</li>
